We are not just about having the idea but committed fully to make it happen. We promise that the first dispatch of orders will be on 10th of September.Thank you for your support!SHENZHEN WATCH & CLOCK QUALITY TEST CENTRE（Founded in 2004,, is one of the most authoritative watch quality inspection organization of China. Meanwhile it’s the first of third party testing organization which owns CNAS and CMA certifications in China.）The ELITE passed the standards of the QB/T 1249-2013<Mechanical Watches>, including 14 quality inspections(Usage reliability、Power reserve、Daily rate、Water resistance test、Cosmetics、Tension resistance.. etc). Test result:Superior Quality Men have always been fascinated by the mechanism working behind the finished product. For this time, we wish to design and create a dress watch that satisfy this pursue of mechanic aesthetics on your wrist while being a perfect fit for the professional elite. This mechanical watch is different. Behind the classic legible dial, you will find the micro-mechanical structure that not only presents the watch with an exquisite delicate appearance but also way less bulky unlike sports and divers watches. The watch aims to present you as a sophisticated specialist at work. Its scratch and wear resistant features along with the stable movement are to help you conquer any occasions. Why is The Elite worth adding to your collection?Is there a micro-rotor watch in your watch collection? Now it’s time to move on! The Elite, with unique movement shape, is distinctive to the mechanical watches you carried. When you open your watchbox and see this watch - it will certainly stand out amongst the rest. The reason of it’s rarity is that processing a micro-rotor movement needs high technology and precision work. The ordinary automatic mechanical movement separates the rotor while the micro-rotor is integrated with other parts of the movement. This technique requires to maintain the aesthetics and stability while reducing some parts of the movement which makes it extra demanding in terms of the internal design and precision of the watch.None collectors don’t want to have such an one-of-a-kind watch in his watch box! It's time to own something different!  At a price of 199 US dollars, we offer the same or even better high-quality materials-sapphire crystal, sturdy stainless steel case, exquisite and stable movement as our competitors, so we believe that we have defeated all of the competitors in this category of watches. And all boderry watches come with a full two-year-warranty.  The dress watch is also our daily tool watch.Before designing, we think that a dress watch should be:
Automatic Mechanical Watch(Saves the trouble of manual winding);
Light-weight and Comfortable to Wear;
Legible Indication;
Wear and Scratch Resistance;
Stability and Accuracy;
  What makes THE ELITE excel in this field? Micro-rotor MovementThe Elite uses a reliable customized Hangzhou AAA-class self-winding 5000B mechanical movement with 30 jewels. It does not need battery to achieve a long-lasting and stable performance. The natural movement of swinging the watch can be converted into energy and powers the watch and enable the watch to store up to 42 hours of energy. You can also manually wind the watch by turning the crown. Quality InspectionFor producing a dress watch, the absolute accuracy is the key on our inspection checklist. Before assembling the watch, we strictly supervise the quality of each part of the components through thorough testings with high standards.We ensure that the accuracy of the watch maintained at -20~+20 sec/day. Unlike regular quality check, we test the watch in 5 more positions to make sure that the watch meets the standard in any situation. Sapphire CrystalSmooth, curvaceous and incredibly sturdy, the watch that you have always imagine. The glass surfaces on the front and back of the watch are made of sapphire crystal with rigidity second to diamond and with excellent scratch resistant. Watch CaseTo increase the durability while maintaining a solid structure, The Elite uses sturdy stainless steel shell. The case is sandblasted to soften all edges and through mold opening, perforation, scouring, sanding and polishing, over 100 procedures were performed on the whole to provide this durable case. Watch DialWhen designing, we wish to maintain the functionality and readability of the watch. This unique floating digital pin took us 3 months to be the final choice. Paired with slender, soft-curved willow hands, the dial looks exceedingly elegant as a whole. Watch BandThe strap is made of cowhide leather and hand-made. The shiny high-quality cowhide ensures that the strap is soft, durable and will not easily peel off. (it will become softer as it is used more often) 50m Water-resistantThe splashes and rain will not stop the watch running. The Elite is 5ATM standard waterproof.How are we going to make this watch?Each piece of The Elite watch is assembled by the masters at our company with their exquisite and skillful craftsmanship who have been working in this field for over 15 years. SHIPPING
To thank the supporters around the world, all orders are free shipping worldwide
